No. 624,

October Term, 1966.

Moody et al. v. Flowers et al., Truman Hobbs on the motion. Cyrus R. Lewis for appellants, in opposition.

387 U. S. 97. Motion of appellees to retax costs granted and the costs are equally divided.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
